1
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:08,540
=Fireworks=

2
00:00:08,540 --> 00:00:10,860
=Episode 9=

3
00:00:16,120 --> 00:00:18,600
Took you long enough to come see me.

4
00:00:19,120 --> 00:00:19,920
I...

5
00:00:21,160 --> 00:00:22,480
I went to find Qiao Nian.

6
00:00:25,079 --> 00:00:26,359
Did you?

7
00:00:32,479 --> 00:00:34,439
Looks like you found her.

8
00:00:39,079 --> 00:00:39,759
Dad,

9
00:00:40,719 --> 00:00:41,799
she's no use

10
00:00:41,799 --> 00:00:43,359
to us anymore.

11
00:00:44,479 --> 00:00:45,799
Qiao Group

12
00:00:46,640 --> 00:00:48,840
is all Qiao Wenjun's now.

13
00:00:50,159 --> 00:00:51,840
Since Qiao Wenjun betrayed us

14
00:00:52,079 --> 00:00:53,119
and sided with Song Group,

15
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:56,920
we can't let those families stay allied.

16
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:04,920
That'll only make Qiao Wenjun stronger.

17
00:01:05,799 --> 00:01:07,000
What's your plan?

18
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:08,599
Destroy their alliance.

19
00:01:14,359 --> 00:01:15,959
Your real goal

20
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:19,560
is helping Qiao Nian
take Qiao Group back, isn't it?

21
00:01:23,879 --> 00:01:25,920
When I sent you to bring her back,

22
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:28,640
I should've known you'd fall for her.

23
00:01:34,079 --> 00:01:37,400
Right now, the real problem
is Qiao Wenjun.

24
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:39,799
She's stopped obeying us.

25
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,920
I need everything you have on her.

26
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:45,840
You worked with her for years.

27
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:48,640
You must have dirt.

28
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:55,640
Dolphi Beauty.

29
00:01:56,719 --> 00:01:59,640
That's the brand she's running now.

30
00:02:00,239 --> 00:02:02,000
The brand Nian built for her mother?

31
00:02:03,359 --> 00:02:04,719
What did Qiao Wenjun do?

32
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:10,120
She's mixing cheap oil
into the premium skincare oil

33
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,520
to cut costs.

34
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:14,759
Customers are already complaining.

35
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:18,319
Got it.

36
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:20,800
I'll look into the factory.

37
00:02:23,759 --> 00:02:24,560
Good.

38
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,759
Do your job well.

39
00:02:41,599 --> 00:02:44,599
I'll arrange for you
to see your brother soon.

40
00:02:45,439 --> 00:02:46,319
My brother?

41
00:02:47,599 --> 00:02:48,360
Hmph!

42
00:02:53,039 --> 00:02:56,319
(Jiang Xiao,
you're not getting away either.)

43
00:02:56,879 --> 00:02:58,360
(Qiao Nian really played this smart.)

44
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,400
(She even recorded it.)

45
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,960
(Duan Yiran, you fool!)

46
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:20,199
Bai Niansheng,
didn't you want to marry Duan Yiran?

47
00:03:20,639 --> 00:03:21,919
Fine. You have my blessing.

48
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:24,080
Take her to America and marry her.

49
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,840
Sorry, Ms. Qiao.

50
00:03:25,879 --> 00:03:27,719
I don't work for Qiao Group anymore.

51
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:30,680
I've joined Jiang Group's US branch.

52
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:31,759
Hey, man.

53
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,390
He's actually pretty handsome.

54
00:03:36,599 --> 00:03:39,599
Bai Niansheng! How dare you betray me!

55
00:03:41,719 --> 00:03:42,520
Come in.

56
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:44,800
Mom.

57
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,280
I promise,

58
00:03:47,479 --> 00:03:49,080
Qiao Nian won't escape this time.

59
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,800
I tied her hands.

60
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:53,240
Not even a fly could get out.

61
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:56,240
A fly?

62
00:04:01,719 --> 00:04:03,800
So this is "not even a fly
could get out"?

63
00:04:06,879 --> 00:04:07,719
That's impossible.

64
00:04:08,319 --> 00:04:09,439
I checked everything.

65
00:04:09,639 --> 00:04:10,960
And what good did that do?

66
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:12,879
This is all over the internet.

67
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,759
Who would still marry you now?

68
00:04:15,919 --> 00:04:16,920
No, Mom.

69
00:04:17,150 --> 00:04:18,279
There's still Bai Niansheng.

70
00:04:18,759 --> 00:04:19,959
He'll still want me.

71
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,920
Don't you dare mention him.

72
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:22,560
Really?

73
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:24,079
You couldn't even hold on to one man.

74
00:04:24,079 --> 00:04:25,800
Now he's run to the Jiangs

75
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:26,839
and turned against me.

76
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:28,319
What good are you?

77
00:04:28,319 --> 00:04:29,000
Useless trash!

78
00:04:29,399 --> 00:04:31,279
No, Mom. That's not true.

79
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,279
Look.

80
00:04:34,839 --> 00:04:35,639
Look.

81
00:04:36,079 --> 00:04:37,000
These rich heirs...

82
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:39,319
I've got them all wrapped
around my finger.

83
00:04:39,319 --> 00:04:40,480
You can use them.

84
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:42,040
Useless. Get off me!

85
00:04:44,639 --> 00:04:45,800
(A bug?)

86
00:04:46,399 --> 00:04:48,319
(Bai Niansheng played you.)

87
00:04:54,879 --> 00:04:56,519
Security, take Duan Yiran

88
00:04:56,519 --> 00:04:58,959
to a psychiatric facility in America.

89
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,360
Without my permission,

90
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:01,600
she doesn't leave.

91
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,000
No! Mom, please!

92
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,079
I can still help you!

93
00:05:04,079 --> 00:05:05,040
I'll behave!

94
00:05:05,399 --> 00:05:06,920
Mom, I can still be useful!

95
00:05:07,519 --> 00:05:08,879
Mom, don't do this!

96
00:05:08,879 --> 00:05:11,000
I'll obey you. I'm useful!

97
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,199
Mom, please!

98
00:05:12,199 --> 00:05:13,720
Mom! Don't!

99
00:05:15,199 --> 00:05:16,279
Qiao Wenjun,

100
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:18,759
you never saw me as your daughter.

101
00:05:25,199 --> 00:05:26,240
Oh, Nian.

102
00:05:26,279 --> 00:05:27,360
You're finally here.

103
00:05:27,399 --> 00:05:28,240
Let me see you.

104
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:36,040
(Jiang Xiao
has been abusing Jiang Zechen.)

105
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:43,079
Dad, Qiao Nian barely made it out
of that fire alive.

106
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,680
She hasn't fully recovered.

107
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:47,759
Oh, right.

108
00:05:47,759 --> 00:05:50,360
I saw the video and got really worried.

109
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:52,079
How are you? Are you okay?

110
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,079
I'm fine.

111
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:56,759
Good.

112
00:05:56,959 --> 00:05:58,040
That's good.

113
00:05:58,660 --> 00:05:59,959
Come on. Don't just stand there.

114
00:05:59,959 --> 00:06:00,759
Come in.

115
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,680
I had the kitchen cook a feast.

116
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:04,680
Come on in.

117
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:06,360
(This man is dangerous.)

118
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:09,560
(If Jiang Zechen
and Qiao Wenjun framed Grandpa,)

119
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:11,879
(he was likely the mastermind.)

120
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:13,720
Qiao Nian, let's go.

121
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:29,959
Zechen.

122
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:34,879
Stay and talk with me for a bit.

123
00:06:40,079 --> 00:06:40,920
Go on home.

124
00:06:41,439 --> 00:06:42,519
Wait for me.

125
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:45,800
Okay. I'll wait for you.

126
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:46,839
Mm.

127
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,720
(That's Mom's bracelet.)

128
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:21,720
There you go, Nian.

129
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:22,240
Mm.

130
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:24,079
See? Pretty, right?

131
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,160
It's beautiful.

132
00:07:25,839 --> 00:07:27,240
These two bracelets

133
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:30,560
can resemble the sound of dolphins.
Hear it?

134
00:07:32,839 --> 00:07:33,560
Wow.

135
00:07:34,399 --> 00:07:35,480
That sound

136
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:38,560
is a mother dolphin calling her baby.

137
00:07:42,519 --> 00:07:44,000
Mom, then does mine

138
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:46,920
sound like a baby dolphin
looking for its mom?

139
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:47,600
Yes.

140
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,160
Nian.

141
00:07:50,160 --> 00:07:50,959
Yeah?

142
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,639
Wherever you are,

143
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:54,160
if you miss me,

144
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:55,720
just shake it.

145
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:57,439
No matter where I am,

146
00:07:58,079 --> 00:07:59,480
I'll hear

147
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,720
and feel it.

148
00:08:00,839 --> 00:08:02,120
Mom, don't say that.

149
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:05,720
We'll never be apart, okay?

150
00:08:08,399 --> 00:08:09,240
It's beautiful.

151
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:13,079
(Mom,)

152
00:08:13,879 --> 00:08:16,399
(why haven't I heard
from you all these years?)

153
00:08:17,079 --> 00:08:18,519
(Where are you?)

154
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:25,439
(Zechen, time to answer for yourself.)

155
00:08:25,839 --> 00:08:27,839
(What have you been hiding from me?)

156
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,120
Get on your knees.

157
00:08:47,919 --> 00:08:49,320
I'll kill you!

158
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:53,759
(What's happening?)

159
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,720
Before I rushed into the fire,

160
00:08:56,519 --> 00:08:58,919
I already felt the searing heat
burning my skin.

161
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:03,960
It must be a shared perception.

162
00:09:05,519 --> 00:09:06,320
(Zechen.)

163
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:16,490
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

164
00:09:16,770 --> 00:09:24,370
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

165
00:09:24,420 --> 00:09:28,210
♪Hearts at play, truth and lies,
who could ever know♪

166
00:09:28,730 --> 00:09:32,010
♪Where this ends♪

167
00:09:32,010 --> 00:09:39,290
♪I try to walk away,
yet still step into the fire♪

168
00:09:39,290 --> 00:09:43,620
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

169
00:09:43,660 --> 00:09:46,740
♪Love turns into pain♪

170
00:09:46,810 --> 00:09:50,930
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

171
00:09:51,090 --> 00:09:54,570
♪Yet I still want you close♪

172
00:09:54,570 --> 00:09:58,740
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

173
00:09:58,740 --> 00:10:02,050
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

174
00:10:02,050 --> 00:10:06,620
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

175
00:10:06,620 --> 00:10:12,930
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪

176
